    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Discretization error achieved level 3 against requirement of 2, providing additional margin. Output comparison NRMSE of 11.3% satisfies the 20% threshold. The CFD model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Uncertainty quantification has been declared applicable to this assessment; sensitivity analysis across operating-point parameters is noted as a recommended enhancement for future MRL 3 assessments but is not required at the current risk level.",
